
;ホームセンターPAGE1
@ITEM_SHOP_WORK_DETAIL_DISPOSABLE

;アイテム名・価格・所持数
PRINTFORML 　《 %ITEMS_ENG(ITEMNAME:SELECT_ITEM)% 》%VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:SELECT_ITEM)%G Owned {ITEM:SELECT_ITEM,2} 
SELECTCASE ITEMNAME:SELECT_ITEM
CASE "栄養ドリンク"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Give Energy Drink or Use Item with owner → Use Item
PRINTL
PRINTL A drug that restores some physical strength.
PRINTL Recovers 20% of the maximum physical strength or 400, whichever is greater.
PRINTL Only one bottle per day can be taken.

CASE "衣服補修布"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Repair Torn Clothes
PRINTFORML ※ requires ＜%ITEMS_ENG("裁縫道具セット")%＞
PRINTL
PRINTL Tool used to mend clothes.
IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
    PRINTL After repair, there is a noticeable color or seam where it was mended
	PRINTL But before you know it, you can no longer tell where it was repaired.
    PRINTL Perhaps it's imbued with some kind of magic.
ENDIF

CASE "ヘアカラー"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Change Hairstyle
PRINTFORML ※ requires ＜%ITEMS_ENG("スタイリング道具セット")%＞
PRINTL
PRINTL A styling product that changes the hair color by applying it to the hair.
IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
    PRINTL I thought there would be a variety of colors, but there's only one,
	PRINTL And if you use it while thinking, "I want it to turn red," it turns red.
    PRINTL Moreover, even if you take a bath, it won't wash out.
    PRINTL Perhaps it contains some kind of magic.
ENDIF

CASE "カラーコンタクト"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Change Eye Color and Shape
PRINTL
PRINTL A fashionable item that changes the appearance of eye color and shape when inserted into the eyes.
IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
    PRINTL I thought there would be a variety of colors, but there's only one,
	PRINTL And if you use it while thinking, "I want it to turn red," it turns red.
    PRINTL Also, if you try to remove them, they don't come off unless you really try,
	PRINTL and they don't have any negative effects even if left in.
    PRINTL Perhaps it contains some kind of magic.
ENDIF

CASE "家畜管理タグ"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Assign New Identity
PRINTL
PRINTL A tag for livestock ears that allows individual management.
PRINTL Normally unnecessary for humans, but by attaching it, you can overwrite one's status.
PRINTL The greatest symbol of humiliation, proof that one has fallen into the status of "slave" or "livestock."

CASE "ハーブティー"
PRINTL ＜Consumable＞
PRINTL Visit → Give Herbal Tea
PRINTL
PRINTL A tea made from herbs from the demon world, with an incredibly powerful relaxing effect.
PRINTL It can restore reason and mental strength, and reduce the chances of falling into a cow-like state.
ENDSELECT


